    "long_instructions": "## Travel Agent - Providing Multiple Examples\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a travel agent by giving the AI a detailed and structured request that includes multiple expectations.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI to recommend a family destination by including **several examples** of vacation destinations.\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the added context improves the accuracy, relevance, and usefulness of the recommendation.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Recommend a vacation destination for a family of four that enjoys outdoor adventures and cultural experiences. For example: \r\n>\r\n> The Bahamas offers beautiful beaches and family-friendly resorts.\r\n>\r\n> OR\r\n> \r\n> Palm Springs offers many nearby hiking opportunities and mini-golf adventures.\r\n>\r\n> OR\r\n> \r\n> Thailand offers jungle excursions and lunar themed parties.\r\n:::",
